<div class="">

  <div class="box">
    <div class="box1">
      <div class="box-div">
        <% if @doctor.photo.attached? %>
            <%= cl_image_tag @doctor.photo.key,gravity: :faces, height: 200, width: 200, crop: :fill %>
          <% else %>
            <%= image_tag "icon.png" , height: 200, width: 200, crop: :fill %>
          <% end %>
        <div class="rate"><br><h5>rating</h5></div>
      </div>

      <div class="box-div-name">
        <h2><%= @doctor.first_name %> <%= @doctor.last_name %></h2>
        <h5>Online Therapy & In Person Therapy</h5>
        <br>
        <h5>Specialization:</h5>
        <h5>Couples Therapy</h5>
      </div>

      <div class="box-div">
      <h5>Contacts:</h5>
      <h5> <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> +32 455 789</h5>
      <h5> <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> <%= @doctor.email %></h5>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="box2">
      <p>Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dicta libero quisquam incidunt eum eligendi ut temporibus a natus. Cupiditate culpa id voluptas possimus cum quidem laudantium repudiandae architecto eveniet doloribus!
        Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Modi eveniet sapiente laudantium, nobis, exercitationem distinctio autem doloribus iure nihil tempora accusamus reprehenderit quos alias obcaecati saepe esse ab maxime natus!</p>
    </div>


    <div class="box3">
      <%= simple_form_for([@doctor, @booking], url: doctor_bookings_path(@doctor)) do |f| %>
      <%= f.input :date, :label => "Choose date",
          as: :string,
          input_html: { data: { controller: "datepicker" } }%>
      <%= f.submit "Book", class: "btn-message" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
